	<p style="text-align: justify">Increases in condom use for pregnancy prevention would simultaneously curb transmission of HIV and other STIs.</p>
	</li>
	<li>
	<p style="text-align: justify">Preventing unwanted pregnancies would increase women's educational and employment opportunities, enhancing their social and economic status.</p>
	</li>
	<li>
